## ✅ Step 4 — Publish to LinkedIn via Blotato

### 1. Set Up Blotato
- Go to [Blotato](https://blotato.com) and create an account.
- Generate a **Blotato API Key** and get your **Account ID**.
- Paste these into the **HTTP Request node** under headers/body:
  - Header: `blotato-api-key: YOUR_API_KEY`
  - Body:
    ```json
    {
      "post": {
        "accountId": "YOUR_ACCOUNT_ID",
        "target": { "targetType": "linkedin" },
        "content": {
          "text": "{{ $('Ask Human for approval').item.json.responseValues.text.value }}",
          "platform": "linkedin",
          "mediaUrls": []
        }
      }
    }
    ```

